<title>HONG KONG: M.C. Packaging shares rise on cash offer.</title>
<headline>M.C. Packaging shares rise on cash offer.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-11-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in M.C. Packaging (Hong Kong) Ltd got a boost on Friday from news that Ball Corp may make a cash offer for the company after buying a controlling stake from Lam Soon (Hong Kong) Ltd, brokers said.</p>
<p>M.C. Packaging shares, which resumed trading after a one-day suspension on Thursday, rose HK$0.075, or 2.91 percent, to HK$2.65 in mid-morning on Friday.</p>
